cs.CE, cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.MS, cs.DL 

The paper discusses the challenges and solutions for reproducibility in computational science, which involves software engineering (cs.SE) for creating and sharing software environments, programming languages (cs.PL) for writing code, and machine learning (cs.MS) and deep learning (cs.DL) for data analysis. The focus is on sustainable computational science, which relates to computational sustainability (cs.CE) that aims to develop computational methods for sustainable development.
